Convert MDX

Use the conversion and remark packages when you want markdown output instead of browser rendering.

```ts import { convertAllMdx } from "@inth/docs/convert"; import { defaultRemarkPlugins, remarkInclude } from "@inth/docs/remark"; await convertAllMdx({ srcDir: "content", outDir: "public", remarkPlugins: [remarkInclude, ...defaultRemarkPlugins], }); ```

